    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "核心模型",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "这是一张<strong>基环树</strong>。每个点 $i$ 只有一条出边指向 $A_i$，不管桶怎么传，它的移动路径是固定的：$B \\to A_B \\to A_{A_B} \\to \\dots$，满足<strong>唯一后效性</strong>。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "因为轮数 $T$ 高达 $10^9$，直接模拟必死。但由于路径固定且信息满足结合律（加法），这是典型的<strong>倍增</strong>应用场景。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "只要看懂题目是在<strong>固定路径</strong>上<strong>跳跃</strong>并<strong>求和</strong>，就能秒出<strong>倍增</strong>解法。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll n, q; cin >> n >> q;\n\tvar p = Vec2<int>(n + 1, 31); // 倍增父节点表\n\tvar dp = Vec2<ll>(n + 1, 31); // 从节点 i 开始，向上跳跃 2 ^ j 步的路径上的信息\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> p[i][0], dp[i][0] = i;\n\tfa(j, 1, 30) {\n\t\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\t\tp[i][j] = p[p[i][j - 1]][j - 1];\n\t\t\tdp[i][j] = dp[i][j - 1] + dp[p[i][j - 1]][j - 1];\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\twhile (q--) {\n\t\tll k, now; cin >> k >> now;\n\t\tll ans = 0;\n\t\tfa(i, 0, 30) {\n\t\t\tif (k & (1ll << i)) {\n\t\t\t\tans += dp[now][i];\n\t\t\t\tnow = p[now][i];\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t\tcout << ans << endl;\n\t}\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
